name: "Aiyneh" Metallic Nail Foils
description:
Dress up your nails with our metallic nail foils, get an amazing look DIY, without spending a fortune at the nail salon!

Comes in a set of 16 pieces.

Silver Metallic Nail Art Foils

Metallic nail art foils add more shines onto your natural or artificial nails! 

Description:

* One sheet of 16 nail art foils in various size: Largest 27x17mm, smallest 27x9mm
* Color: Silver.
* Self adhensive, easy to use and long lasting.
* Note: The nail art foils will come alone, there's No nail art tool in our package.

How to use:

* Remove the old nail polish.
* Push back the cuticle & buff the nails to make a clean & smooth surface.
* Select the right size nail foil and trim for your nail.
* Put it on, rub and smooth it firmly onto the nails.
  (possibly with heating to make it smoother).
* Cut off the nail foil to the free edge, and use a file in a gentle downward motion to remove the excess nail foil and make it fit to the natural free edge.
* Seal it with either Acrylic or UV Gel for longer time lasting.
